        {
            "title": "美國企業活動擴張速度創下今年次高水平 得益於訂單成長強勁",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 受訂單強勁成長推動，美國10月企業活動擴張速度創下今年以來第二高。為刺激銷售，企業在定價方面更加克制。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">標普全球周五公佈的數據顯示，10月綜合產出指數初值上漲近1點，至54.8。該指數高於50表明經濟活動處於擴張區間。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">新訂單綜合指標升至54.2，為今年以來最高水平。訂單成長主要受到製造業訂單量創去年2月以來最強勁增幅推動。服務業方面，新業務擴張也創下2024年底以來最大成長。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「數據表明第四季度開局經濟成長持續強勁，製造業與服務業的商業活動均呈現出加速勢頭，」標普全球市場情報的首席商業經濟學家Chris Williamson在聲明中表示。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-c800e3dd-03ac-3c0f-915f-d8361efa60b3-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">不過，調查報告的細分數據呈現出更多分化跡象。雖然工廠產出成長有所加快，但製造業就業指標降至三個月低點。服務業就業成長僅略快於前月。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本月衡量原物料支付價格的綜合指標小幅上升，但仍維持在60.8的高位；相比之下，銷售價格指標增速為六個月以來最慢，Williamson指出，這表明企業正在通過價格競爭來爭取訂單。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">與此同時，訂單積壓情況基本停滯，出口新訂單出現六個月來最大降幅，這與企業更積極的降價策略相一致。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Business Activity Expands at Second-Fastest Pace This Year</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E4%BC%81%E6%A5%AD%E6%B4%BB%E5%8B%95%E6%93%B4%E5%BC%B5%E9%80%9F%E5%BA%A6%E5%89%B5%E4%B8%8B%E4%BB%8A%E5%B9%B4%E6%AC%A1%E9%AB%98%E6%B0%B4%E5%B9%B3-%E5%BE%97%E7%9B%8A%E6%96%BC%E8%A8%82%E5%96%AE%E6%88%90%E9%95%B7%E5%BC%B7%E5%8B%81-143408758.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-24 23:25:52",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "通用汽車裁員逾200人 降本增效應對關稅逆風",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> <a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:通用汽車;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/通用汽車\">通用汽車</a>周五裁減數百個崗位，就在幾日前該公司上調全年利潤指引推動股價大漲。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">據知情人士透露，通用汽車解雇了超過200名受薪員工，主要集中在密西根州沃倫市的技術中心。因討論未公開信息而要求匿名的知情人士表示，消息於上午7點左右傳達，公司通過Slack頻道通知部分受影響員工，稱此次裁員出於「業務狀況」考慮，與個人業績無關。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">在汽車製造商努力應對美國總統川普不斷變化的政策之際，通用汽車一直在精簡架構以提高利潤。儘管關稅推高了成本，但車企大多未能通過提價來抵消。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-410fdaea-6cd4-3c46-a29b-a364e8679ffe-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">通用汽車在本周早些時候公佈了優於預期的第三季度財報，推動公司股價錄得逾五年來最大單日漲幅。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題GM Cuts Hundreds of Salaried Workers as Part of Profit Push (1)</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E9%80%9A%E7%94%A8%E6%B1%BD%E8%BB%8A%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E9%80%BE200%E4%BA%BA-%E9%99%8D%E6%9C%AC%E5%A2%9E%E6%95%88%E6%87%89%E5%B0%8D%E9%97%9C%E7%A8%85%E9%80%86%E9%A2%A8-140318973.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-24 22:55:56",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "美國消費者信心指數跌至五個月低點 通膨擔憂幾乎未見緩解",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 10月美國消費者信心降至五個月低點，反映出人們對居高不下的物價及其對個人財務影響的擔憂仍未緩解。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">根據<a class=\"link\" data-i13n=\"sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link\" data-ylk=\"slk:密西根大學;sec:content-canvas;subsec:anchor_text;elm:context_link;itc:0\" href=\"https://hk.finance.yahoo.com/tag/密西根大學\">密西根大學</a>周五公佈的數據，10月消費者信心指數終值從9月的55.1下滑至53.6，低於本月早先公佈的初值。衡量當前經濟狀況的指標降至2022年8月以來最低水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">調查顯示，消費者預計未來5到10年物價年均上漲3.9%，高於上月預期的3.7%。對於未來一年的通膨預期則略有回落，從上月的4.7%降至4.6%。</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-fe7c298b-83e5-3a52-af28-ba395d787053-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「總體而言，消費者認為當前經濟狀況與上月變化不大；通膨和高物價依然是人們最關心的問題，」密西根大學消費者調查負責人Joanne Hsu在聲明中表示。「本月幾乎沒有跡象表明消費者將聯邦政府停擺與經濟狀況聯繫起來。」</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">當天早些時候公佈的數據顯示，9月CPI升幅低於預期，但家庭支出情況不一。儘管雜物價格漲幅放緩，但穀物和無酒精飲料等主要商品的價格卻出現反彈。汽油價格上漲，汽車保險價格有所回落。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">密西根大學的調查指出，消費者「對物價居高不下感到沮喪」，近一半受訪者表示個人財務狀況受到影響。儘管對就業市場的預期本月保持穩定，但仍處於相對悲觀的水平。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">調查還顯示，現狀指標降至多年低點58.6，大件商品的購買景氣度指標降至自2022年以來的最低水平。消費者預期指標滑落至50.3，創五個月新低。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">本輪調查時間為9月23日至10月20日。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題US Consumer Sentiment Drops to Five-Month Low on Price Concerns</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
            "link": "https://hk.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E6%B6%88%E8%B2%BB%E8%80%85%E4%BF%A1%E5%BF%83%E6%8C%87%E6%95%B8%E8%B7%8C%E8%87%B3%E4%BA%94%E5%80%8B%E6%9C%88%E4%BD%8E%E9%BB%9E-%E9%80%9A%E8%86%A8%E6%93%94%E6%86%82%E5%B9%BE%E4%B9%8E%E6%9C%AA%E8%A6%8B%E7%B7%A9%E8%A7%A3-142022527.html",
            "pub_date": "2025-10-24 23:25:54",
            "source": "yahoo_finance_asia",
            "kind": 1,
            "language": "zh-HK"
        },
        {
            "title": "印度據悉接近與美國敲定貿易協議 但強調不會倉促簽署",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"10月24日，Piyush Goyal在柏林\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/kaThwvotaSheRAf7294ECA--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/5243b7a2461abf6d55bcbef8a208a180\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">10月24日，Piyush Goyal在柏林</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><br/></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\"><span class=\"news-dateline\">【彭博】--</span> 一位政府官員表示，印度接近與美國敲定貿易協定，雙方在大多數議題上接近達成一致。儘管印度商務部長強調，新德里不會倉促簽署任何協議。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">因討論未公開消息而要求匿名的知情官員表示，大多數問題已趨於一致，雙方達成協議在望。而印度商務部長Piyush Goyal早些時候稱，印度不會迫於壓力達成協議。</p><div class=\"recommendation-contents\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mb-2 h-[30px] w-[80px] rounded-lg\"></div><div class=\"no-scrollbar -mx-5 mb-5 flex overflow-hidden overflow-x-auto md:-mx-2 lg:mb-3.5\"><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mr-2 ml-5 h-[92px] w-[calc(85%-28px)] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg md:ml-2 md:w-[calc(85%-16px)] lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div><div class=\"bg-marshmallow mx-2 h-[92px] w-[85%] flex-shrink-0 rounded-lg lg:h-[120px] lg:w-[calc(50%-16px)]\"></div></div></div><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit\"><img alt=\"10月24日，Piyush Goyal在柏林Photographer: Krisztian Bocsi/Bloomberg\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"640\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WZJaTX7faE8mZRY4HBjIbQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtoPTY0MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://media.zenfs.com/en/bloomberg_chinese_traditional_757/5fb4ff81e32457b31a618ebef5207d51\" width=\"960\"/><figcaption class=\"text-px14 text-dolphin mt-2 wrap-anywhere\" style=\"max-width:960px\">10月24日，Piyush Goyal在柏林Photographer: Krisztian Bocsi/Bloomberg</figcaption></div></figure><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">「我們不會倉促達成交易，也不會在最後期限或壓力下達成交易，」Goyal在德國柏林出席活動時表示。「我們已經接受，如果要對我們徵收關稅，那就征吧。」</p><div class=\"bg-card-bg-1 -mx-5 -mt-2 mb-3 pb-3 md:-mx-0\"><div class=\"text-px14 text-gandalf py-1 text-center leading-5\">廣告</div><div class=\"mx-auto text-center min-w-[300px] min-h-[250px]\" id=\"sda-inbody-52040026-7820-39c8-be49-64735d2cbe95-1-iframe\"><div class=\"bg-dirty-seagull text-px12 text-dolphin mx-auto hidden items-center justify-center only:flex w-[300px] h-[250px]\">廣告</div></div></div><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">美國總統唐納德·川普以印度購買俄羅斯石油且不願擴大美國產品市場准入為由，對印度實施了50%的懲罰性關稅。華盛頓方面要求新德里停止所有俄羅斯進口，這是達成貿易協議的關鍵條件。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">這位知情官員表示，雙方談判代表通過線上會議就協議的法律用語進行磋商，最終決定需由兩國領導層作出。</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">原文標題India Signals US Trade Deal Even as Minister Says It Won’t Rush</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">--聯合報導 Savio Shetty.</p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">More stories like this are available on <a class=\"link\" data-ylk=\"slk:bloomberg.com;elm:context_link;itc:0;sec:content-canvas\" href=\"https://www.bloomberg.com\" rel=\"nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">bloomberg.com</a></p><p class=\"mb-module-gap break-words leading-[1.4] text-px20 lg:text-px18 lg:leading-[1.8] text-batcave\">©2025 Bloomberg L.P.</p></div>",
